"title": "4035: abundance",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4035",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A state of plenty. Since Israel was often restricted in resources, abundance was an important feature of her future hope, and became a symbol of spiritual well-being.</p>\n<h2>Examples of material abundance</h2>\n<h3>Rain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:2\">DEU 32:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:41\">1KI 18:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:45\">1KI 18:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:28\">JOB 36:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:9\">PSA 68:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:23\">JOL 2:23</a></p>\n<h3>Water, streams and rivers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:20\">PSA 78:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:7\">NUM 24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:4\">2CH 32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:3\">PSA 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:4\">ISA 44:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:5\">EZK 47:5</a></p>\n<h3>Luxuriant growth and fruitfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:12\">EZK 47:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:10\">EZK 19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:2-Ezek31:9\">EZK 31:2–31:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:12\">DAN 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:21\">DAN 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:2\">REV 22:2</a></p>\n<h3>Harvest, food, milk and wine</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:13\">AMO 9:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:10\">2CH 31:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:7\">PSA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:5\">PSA 23:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:19\">PSA 37:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:10\">PRO 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:22\">ISA 7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:17\">JER 44:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:13\">JOL 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:11\">MIC 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>Spaciousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:8\">PSA 31:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:22\">GEN 26:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:12\">PSA 66:12</a></p>\n<h3>Wealth and possessions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:35\">GEN 24:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:43\">GEN 30:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen36:7\">GEN 36:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:32\">2SA 19:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:15\">2CH 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:22\">2CH 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:3\">JOB 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Canaan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:8\">EXO 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:27\">NUM 13:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:8\">DEU 8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:7\">JER 2:7</a></p>\n<h2>Material abundance a reward for obedience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:5\">LEV 26:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:9\">DEU 30:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:12\">JOB 42:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:15\">PSA 132:15</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience not always rewarded in this way</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:12\">JOB 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:6\">JOB 2:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:12\">PHP 4:12</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of spiritual abundance</h2>\n<h3>The abundance of divine power</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:26\">DEU 9:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:4\">PSA 93:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:29-Joel2:32\">JOL 2:29–2:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18-Eph1:20\">EPH 1:18–1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:20\">EPH 3:20</a></p>\n<h3>The abundance of divine grace</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:20\">ROM 5:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:8-2Cor9:14\">2CO 9:8–9:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:7\">EPH 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:6-Eph2:7\">EPH 2:6–2:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:14\">1TI 1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:2\">2PE 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>The abundance of human thanksgiving</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:15\">2CO 4:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:171\">PSA 119:171</a></p>\n<h3>The abundance of God's future blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17\">2CO 4:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:8\">PSA 36:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:4\">ISA 64:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:10\">JHN 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:9\">1CO 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:11\">2PE 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:3\">REV 14:3</a></p>",
